{"type":"message","id":"350be6e5","parentId":"65feafc5","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:47:44.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说求出的 L-LENGTH = 4102，这和我之前计算的 STBC 模式下的结果 2638 不一致。我需要重新检查计算过程。\n\n让我重新思考这个问题：\n\n用户的参数：\n- 帧格式：HE TB\n- InfoBytes = 990（N_data_bits）\n- MCS = 1（QPSK, R=1/2）\n- STBC_mode = 1\n- 4x HE-LTF\n- 3.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775115869856,"responseId":"aa4f05f836fe3f9e367ca2e93b5ec59b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dbcd5b59","parentId":"350be6e5","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:41:59.640Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53d6f3a690a8c4fb0dcd054cef6\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 16:41 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b53d6f3a690a8c4fb0dcd054cef6]\nou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf: 查看wifi6协议，告诉我HE TB OFDMA stbc场景下，有没有要求data符号个数必须是偶数，有的话请告诉我在哪一章节实现的？"}],"timestamp":1775119319637}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6aecee6","parentId":"dbcd5b59","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:42:14.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问 WiFi 6 (802.11ax) 协议中，HE TB OFDMA STBC 场景下是否有要求 data 符号个数必须是偶数的规定，如果有的话需要告诉他在哪个章节。\n\n这是一个非常具体的协议问题，涉及到 STBC 编码的特性。STBC（Space-Time Block Coding）通常需要偶数个符号来进行完整的 Alamouti 编码，因为在 STBC 中，两个符号会被组合编码到两个时空流上。\n\n我需要搜索 802.11ax 协议相关的内容来回答这个问题。让我先搜索一下相关信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_58203a6fa67b4980898bf4a4","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"802.11ax HE TB OFDMA STBC even number symbols N_SYM requirement specification"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":29113,"output":275,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29388,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775119319639,"responseId":"2696d2dee47755d042d187bf05e0859e"}}
