\"mentor.ieee.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2128178d51d28666\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n[XLS] Comments - IEEE Mentor\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2128178d51d28666\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://mentor.ieee.org/802.11/dcn/18/11-18-0619-07-000m-revmd-editor2-lb232-comments.xlsx\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c270b0721caed704\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n... clause like clause 27 of the 802.11ax draft. As in the comment. REJECTED (GEN: 2018-04-10 14:58:56Z) The 802.11 Editor's have considered. The 802.11ax use ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c270b0721caed704\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"mentor.ieee.org\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"\"802.11ax\" \"27.3.11\" OR \"clause 27\" STBC N_SYM even \"symbol pairs\"","provider":"firecrawl","count":3,"tookMs":1686,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"firecrawl","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6042a87cf2a1098c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n[XLS] Comments - IEEE Mentor\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"6042a87cf2a1098c\">>>","url":"https://mentor.ieee.org/802.11/dcn/19/11-19-1782-00-00ax-comments-on-d5-0.xlsx","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"06529b445b1e9a4d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFor the purposes of starting discussion on this issue, I would like to propose that the ED threshold for 802.11ax operation in the 6 GHz band be changed from - ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"06529b445b1e9a4d\">>>","siteName":"mentor.ieee.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"9299bdefb0450adb\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n[XLS] Comments - IEEE Mentor\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"9299bdefb0450adb\">>>","url":"https://mentor.ieee.org/802.11/dcn/20/11-20-0241-10-00ax-sa1-comments-on-tgax-d6-0.xlsx","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4b08ce6d65564