{"type":"message","id":"8bd60db5","parentId":"bab48ce4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:43:43.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索结果还是没有直接找到具体的协议条款。让我换个思路，根据我对 WiFi 协议的了解，STBC (Space-Time Block Coding) 确实需要对符号进行配对处理。在 802.11n/ac/ax 中，STBC 使用 Alamouti 编码方案，这要求符号必须成对处理。\n\n让我根据协议知识来回答用户的问题。在 802.11ax (WiFi 6) 中：\n- STBC 使用 Alamouti 编码\n- Alamouti 编码需要两个符号组成一对进行处理\n- 因此数据符号数 N_SYM 在 STBC 模式下应该是偶数\n\n但我需要找到具体的协议条款来确认这一点。让我再搜索一下相关的技术文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d75e99f9438945109a9efdd4","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"802.11ax STBC Alamouti encoding symbol pairs N_SYM_MOD even number"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":49279,"output":332,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49611,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775119404228,"responseId":"4ce3035b52bd6f32b2b0701a45e00a95"}}
